\begin_inset Formula $T_{i}\sim\Gamma\left(k_{i},\theta_{i}\right)$
\end_inset

, a 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

-dimensional vector of positive numbers 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha\in\left(\mathbb{R}_{+}^{*}\right)^{n}$
\end_inset

 and 
