\[
Z=T\bigg|\sum_{i}\alpha_{i}T_{i}=d
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
We define this distribution over the 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

-dimensional simplex 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
